{"tid":1124616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【吐痰發爛】囂張支那女大鬧台灣小店：你們是殖民地！","createTime":"2019-04-25T06:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T07:01:05.000Z","uid":92301,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"da6edadf178115b28a1d694ac994062c97404aaa","tid":1124616,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"這名強國女實在太囂張了！她日前到台北著名的饒河夜市的一間冰店，闖入冰店的櫃枱，想要下單，老闆於是便用國語「請」她離去，沒想到女遊客聽不明白，突然發難，對老闆說：「不准講方言！」更在店內吐痰，大罵：「你們是中國附屬的！說你們是殖民地就是殖民地！一個破破爛爛的省！」，老闆反罵她說「你們國家都這樣吐痰的？」國女竟回答說：「我們國家都這種風格！」<br />\n<br />\n這名冰店姓郭的老闆，對台灣《蘋果新聞網》講述事發經過。他說這名大陸女遊客到他的店裏，沒開口點東西，便衝到櫃枱後面。由於冰店是前舖後居，加上當時正在開火煮東西，郭男擔心她受傷，便請她離開，到店外下單。沒想到這名大陸女便開始發難叫囂，並且不斷的吐痰。<br />\n<br />\n這名大陸女說：「我又不是你們這邊的人，我怎麼知道不能進來？」郭男開始不耐煩，對她說：「要教訓人到你們國家去嘛！丟臉丟到外國！」這刻大陸女彷彿聽到「關鍵字」，再吐兩口痰，越罵越兇：「甚麼你們國家我們國家？你們是中國附屬的！」更說郭男的台灣國語是「方言」不許他再說，更說：「你們台灣有幾個能賺錢養活自己？都靠大陸的福利來支持你們！」<br />\n<br />\n郭男不甘示弱，對大陸女說：「你們國家都這樣吐痰的？」沒想到大陸女竟回答：「我們國家都這種風格！」在場者都看得傻眼，郭男便說：「我們國家吐痰要罰錢，我們是有教育的！」大陸女之後嘰嘰喳喳的在叫囂，這時警察接到，到冰店了解。<br />\n<br />\n大陸女見到警察，態度180度轉變，馬上收聲，拿出證件給警察檢查，發現這名女子姓石，自稱是跟旅行團到台灣。警員見狀，對石女作嚴正警告，郭男向警方稱不作追究，也不做她的生意，石女才悻悻然離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190425/59523078?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190425%2F59523078%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SaRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=85596a0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190425%2F59523078%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=3b64dec4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190425/59523078?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"77ec5bc9f09eec9aefb3828bc8bd7b83bd15bf87","tid":1124616,"uid":200911,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們國家都這種風格</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f56c596913756fafdcb5d8f95b8171db465be2","tid":1124616,"uid":39365,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"77ec5bc9f09eec9aefb3828bc8bd7b83bd15bf87","tid":1124616,"uid":200911,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:25:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們國家都這種風格</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"民進黨應免費俾佢去高雄玩"},{"pid":"4a4ad05ad4abbe123cb5e98a23fb43c0c422fba4","tid":1124616,"uid":27411,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:33:48.000Z","msg":"佢係咪去錯地方，中華民國係獨立國家嚟，香港先係佢國家既殖民地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe4915b0c7fc45531bde61fe9ac521734616392","tid":1124616,"uid":1425,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"佢又冇講錯喎, 係講早左年幾姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d93899880bc2aefe6234ffa43b67e07e26e700","tid":1124616,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"唔追究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9456d52ae8f8e3406b87e8384bebf67b358c6879","tid":1124616,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T01:59:3